<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="sigh-vi">sigh <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /saɪ/    美 /saɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>叹息；叹气；悲叹：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>sighed with relief</strong> and agreed to meet her at the convenience store down the road.
我如释重负地松了口气，同意和她在街上的便利店见面。</p><footer>北师大⑤ – 13</footer></div></div>